==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scalebeam
<hw>Scale"beam`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
lever or beam of a balance; the lever of a platform scale, to which the
poise for weighing is applied.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A weighing apparatus with a sliding weight,
resembling a steelyard.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scaleboard</ent>⟦br⟧
